{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/blog/2020/abem/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"lannex"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"4e152952-ca54-56b6-8788-f84b29856219","excerpt":"…","html":"<p>많은 분들이 소프트웨어에서 아키텍처와 디자인은 늘 중요하다고는 말하지만 잘 간과하곤 합니다.\n사실 그렇게 간과하더라도 추상적으로, 그리고 말로만 알고 있는 그 중요성을 새로운 기능 추가 및 수정을 비롯한 다양한 요구사항을 겪으며 여러 프로젝트를 거치다보면 결국에는 알게 됩니다.</p>\n<p><strong>거의 모든 것을 아키텍처와 디자인이 좌우한다</strong>라는 것을 말입니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"왜-중요할까\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%99%9C-%EC%A4%91%EC%9A%94%ED%95%A0%EA%B9%8C\" aria-label=\"왜 중요할까 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>왜 중요할까?</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>빨리가는 유일한 방법은 제대로 가는 것이다.</p>\n<p>- 로버트 C 마틴</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>이는 결국 효율성, 그리고 생산성의 이야기입니다. 제대로 된 아키텍처와 디자인일수록 소프트웨어의 복잡도는 줄어들고 변경이나 추가되는 기능들의 개발을 더욱더 수월하게 만듭니다.\n뿐만아니라 협업을 하는 당사자들간의 의사소통을 원활하게 해줍니다. 그리고 위험요소를 최소화할 수 있으며 미래의 불확실성 또한 줄일 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p>이런 이유로 이번 주제는 Front-end에서 UI 컴포넌트의 시스템 구축에 쓰이는 디자인 방법론을 얘기하고자 합니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"atomic-design\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#atomic-design\" aria-label=\"atomic design permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Atomic Design</h2>\n<p><img src=\"/75573eea54c91def7c03edb1dead25e3/atomic-design.svg\" alt=\"Atomic\"></p>\n<p>Atomic Design이란 브래드 프로스트라는 디자이너가 2013년에 제시한 개념이자 방법론입니다. 딱히 소프트웨어를 염두하고 만든 것은 아니나 컴포넌트 단위로 개발되는 Front-end의 UI 계층을 디자인하는데는 안성맞춤이라 널리 퍼지게 되었습니다.</p>\n<p>Atomic Design은 Atoms(원자), Molecules(분자), Organisms(유기체), Templates(템플릿), Pages(페이지)로 구성됩니다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"atoms-원자\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#atoms-%EC%9B%90%EC%9E%90\" aria-label=\"atoms 원자 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Atoms (원자)</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>UI의 최소 단위</li>\n<li>재사용을 위한 최소 단위이니 가장 단순 역할을 담당해야함</li>\n<li>Button이나 Input, Label과 같은 기초적인 컴포넌트</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ce6bcfc1b1cc072924365ec2d5f6e7e3/29007/atoms.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Atoms\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/ce6bcfc1b1cc072924365ec2d5f6e7e3/5a190/atoms.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ce6bcfc1b1cc072924365ec2d5f6e7e3/772e8/atoms.png 200w,\n/static/ce6bcfc1b1cc072924365ec2d5f6e7e3/e17e5/atoms.png 400w,\n/static/ce6bcfc1b1cc072924365ec2d5f6e7e3/5a190/atoms.png 800w,\n/static/ce6bcfc1b1cc072924365ec2d5f6e7e3/c1b63/atoms.png 1200w,\n/static/ce6bcfc1b1cc072924365ec2d5f6e7e3/29007/atoms.png 1600w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"molecules-분자\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#molecules-%EB%B6%84%EC%9E%90\" aria-label=\"molecules 분자 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Molecules (분자)</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>2개 이상의 Atom으로 구성되어 그룹화된 컴포넌트</li>\n<li>Atom의 결합으로 보다 구체적인 작은 블록 형태</li>\n<li>InputGroup = Input + Label</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/aaf4ff47291c30933a57611ca3f1dda1/29007/molecules.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Molecules\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/aaf4ff47291c30933a57611ca3f1dda1/5a190/molecules.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/aaf4ff47291c30933a57611ca3f1dda1/772e8/molecules.png 200w,\n/static/aaf4ff47291c30933a57611ca3f1dda1/e17e5/molecules.png 400w,\n/static/aaf4ff47291c30933a57611ca3f1dda1/5a190/molecules.png 800w,\n/static/aaf4ff47291c30933a57611ca3f1dda1/c1b63/molecules.png 1200w,\n/static/aaf4ff47291c30933a57611ca3f1dda1/29007/molecules.png 1600w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"organisms-유기체\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#organisms-%EC%9C%A0%EA%B8%B0%EC%B2%B4\" aria-label=\"organisms 유기체 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Organisms (유기체)</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Molecule과 Atom을 조합하여 하나의 큰 블록 형태</li>\n<li>큰 단위의 시작점이라 여기서부터는 재사용성이 다소 떨어짐</li>\n<li>Header = InputGroup + Menu+ Button</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/15231e6ac3ed74f20229d6b41209f39d/29007/organisms.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Organisms\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/15231e6ac3ed74f20229d6b41209f39d/5a190/organisms.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/15231e6ac3ed74f20229d6b41209f39d/772e8/organisms.png 200w,\n/static/15231e6ac3ed74f20229d6b41209f39d/e17e5/organisms.png 400w,\n/static/15231e6ac3ed74f20229d6b41209f39d/5a190/organisms.png 800w,\n/static/15231e6ac3ed74f20229d6b41209f39d/c1b63/organisms.png 1200w,\n/static/15231e6ac3ed74f20229d6b41209f39d/29007/organisms.png 1600w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"templates-템플릿\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#templates-%ED%85%9C%ED%94%8C%EB%A6%BF\" aria-label=\"templates 템플릿 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Templates (템플릿)</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>레이아웃으로 하나의 틀이자 설계도</li>\n<li>배치되거나 포함된 컴퍼넌트가 없는 페이지의 골격 구조</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b0c1c658e8961b64d8b7a70b154bf0c7/29007/templates.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Templates\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/b0c1c658e8961b64d8b7a70b154bf0c7/5a190/templates.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b0c1c658e8961b64d8b7a70b154bf0c7/772e8/templates.png 200w,\n/static/b0c1c658e8961b64d8b7a70b154bf0c7/e17e5/templates.png 400w,\n/static/b0c1c658e8961b64d8b7a70b154bf0c7/5a190/templates.png 800w,\n/static/b0c1c658e8961b64d8b7a70b154bf0c7/c1b63/templates.png 1200w,\n/static/b0c1c658e8961b64d8b7a70b154bf0c7/29007/templates.png 1600w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"pages-페이지\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#pages-%ED%8E%98%EC%9D%B4%EC%A7%80\" aria-label=\"pages 페이지 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Pages (페이지)</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Template에 Atom, Molecule, Organism을 배치한 완성본</li>\n<li>Template이라는 일종의 양식이 적용된 최종 산출물</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7bf47a16c2802b6ed257a2599f64cd6b/b17f8/pages.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Pages\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/7bf47a16c2802b6ed257a2599f64cd6b/4b190/pages.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7bf47a16c2802b6ed257a2599f64cd6b/e07e9/pages.jpg 200w,\n/static/7bf47a16c2802b6ed257a2599f64cd6b/066f9/pages.jpg 400w,\n/static/7bf47a16c2802b6ed257a2599f64cd6b/4b190/pages.jpg 800w,\n/static/7bf47a16c2802b6ed257a2599f64cd6b/e5166/pages.jpg 1200w,\n/static/7bf47a16c2802b6ed257a2599f64cd6b/b17f8/pages.jpg 1600w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"bem\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#bem\" aria-label=\"bem permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>BEM</h2>\n<p>BEM (Block Element Modifier)은 CSS를 보다 쉽게 유지 관리 할 수 도와주는 CSS 디자인 방법론입니다. 네이밍 컨벤션이기도 하는 BEM은 CSS를 다루는 것이라 이미 예전부터 많은 곳에서 사용되고 있습니다.</p>\n<p>BEM은 단어 구분을 kebab-case로 사용하며 그 이름과 같게 Block, Element, Modifier로 구성되어 있습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>form</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>form form--theme-xmas form--simple<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>form__input<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span>\n    <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>form__submit form__submit--disabled<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>submit<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>form</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.form</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.form--theme-xmas</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.form--simple</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.form__input</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.form__submit</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.form__submit--disabled</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"block\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#block\" aria-label=\"block permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Block</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>독립적인 단위</li>\n<li>클래스 첫머리에 위치</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"element\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#element\" aria-label=\"element permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Element</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Block에 일부이며 종속적</li>\n<li>독립적인 의미는 없음</li>\n<li>Block과 Element 사이는 Underscore를 사용</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"modifier\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#modifier\" aria-label=\"modifier permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Modifier</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Block 또는 Element에 대한 플래그, 동작 또는 상태를 변경하는데 사용</li>\n<li>속성이라고 할 수 있음</li>\n<li>Element와 Modifier 사이는 두개의 Hyphen을 사용</li>\n<li>클래스 끝머리에 위치</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"abem\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#abem\" aria-label=\"abem permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ABEM</h2>\n<p>ABEM은 Atomic Design과 BEM의 조합입니다. BEM의 단점인 긴 Modifier를 축약형으로 바꾸고 클래스 첫머리를 Atomic일 경우 <code class=\"language-text\">a-</code>, Molecule일 경우 <code class=\"language-text\">b-</code> 와 같이 각각의 단위 첫글자를 따서 사용합니다.</p>\n<p>그리고 단어 구분을 kebab-case를 사용하는대신 camelCase를 사용합니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- BEM --></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>block-name__element-name block-name__element-name--small block-name__element-name--green block-name__element-name--active<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  Submit\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- ABEM --></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>a-blockName__elementName -small -green -active<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  Submit\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"정리\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC\" aria-label=\"정리 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>정리</h2>\n<p>빠르게 변화하는 개발 환경 속에 더 나은 방법론이 대두될 수도 혹은 직접 만들 수도 있습니다.\n직접 원칙을 정한 설계가 물론 더 좋을 순 있지만 Atomic Design + BEM을 도입함으로써 그 고민의 과정을 좀 더 줄일 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p>어떻게 구조를 설계해야 할 지 고민하고 있다면 Atomic Design + BEM을 한번 도입해보는 게 어떨런지요?</p>\n<h2 id=\"참고-자료\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0-%EC%9E%90%EB%A3%8C\" aria-label=\"참고 자료 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>참고 자료</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://bradfrost.com/blog/post/atomic-web-design/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://bradfrost.com/blog/post/atomic-web-design/</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://getbem.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">http://getbem.com/</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Atomic Design과 BEM (ABEM)","date":"2020-11-20","description":"ABEM = Atomic Design + BEM","tags":["javascript","react"]}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/2020/abem/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2020/es2016-es2020/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"ES2016에서 